title: Jane's F-15 & F/A-18
description:
Considered some of the most realistic fighter sim ever (alongside the Falcon and Flanker series), Jane's Combat Simulation presents F-15 and F/A-18. In F-15, the player flies the F-15E Strike Eagle while in F/A-18 the player flies the F/A-18E Super Hornet. The aircrafts which the player flies are considered to be meticulously detailed and very accurate.

To install, simply mount, install (use compatibility mode for Vista/Seven users), then apply patch.

Language: English
